To Release
----------

Prerequisities:
* libdevel-cover-perl (Devel::Cover)
* libtemplate-perl (Template::Toolkit)
* libtest-pod-coverage-perl (Test::Pod::Coverage)
* libppi-html-perl (PPI::HTML)
* libhtml-parser-perl (HTML::Parser and HTML::Entities)
* libmodule-build-perl (Module::Build)
* cpanminus (App::cpanminus)
  - XML::Entities
  - Minilla

(Notes.)

Commit all changes.

Run tests:
for t in t/*.t; do
  perl -Ilib "$t"
done

Bump version in:
	Writer.pm
	Writer/Encoding.pm

Update changelog.

git commit -a

Locally,

# Create a distribution from the tag
minil release

# Generate coverage report for the new release
perl Build.PL
cover -test -report Html_basic -outputdir coverage

Upload to CPAN.

Update web page:
mkdir temp-website

web/gen-index.pl >temp-website/index.html
cp web/style.css temp-website/

cp -pr coverage temp-website/

cd temp-website
git init
git add .
git commit -m 'Generated website.'

git push -f git@github.com:josephw/xml-writer-perl.git master:refs/heads/gh-pages
